{"id":"21043","name":"两个人的演唱会","rarity":4,"path":"Knight","desc":"「哥哥，这是……」 \n「好久没有快乐地唱过歌了吧…我为你搭了一座舞台，就是…有点简陋。」 \n「可老师觉得我不适合……」 \n「不，我觉得很好听！以后你一定会实现自己的梦想，站在更大的舞台上歌唱……」 \n……\n许多年之后，她站在璀璨的舞台上，望着底下汹涌的粉丝，却失神了片刻——\n在漫长的追梦路上，她总会想起那道信任的目光，和自己的第一场「演唱会」。\n没有绚丽的灯光，没有华美的妆造，有的只是一个孩子为了鼓励另一个孩子追求梦想而搭建起的舞台。\n「如今，我们的梦都实现了。但…那还是属于『我们』的梦吗……」 \n她握紧了话筒。在下一首歌开始之前，她甚至来不及感到悲伤。","icon":"icon/light_cone/21043.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/21043.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/21043.png","guide_overview":[],"ranks":{"id":"21043","skill":"鼓舞","desc":"使装备者的防御力提高#1[i]%。场上每有一名持有护盾的角色，装备者造成的伤害提高#2[i]%。","params":[[0.16,0.04],[0.2,0.05],[0.24,0.06],[0.28,0.07],[0.32,0.08]],"properties":[[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.16}],[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.2}],[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.24}],[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.28}],[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.32}]]},"promotions":{"id":"21043","values":[{"hp":{"base":43.2,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":16.8,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":21,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":95.04,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":36.96,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":46.2,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":164.16,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":63.84,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":79.8,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":233.28,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":90.72,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":113.4,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":302.4,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":117.6,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":147,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":371.52,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":144.48,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":180.6,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":440.64,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":171.36,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":214.2,"step":3.15}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":4000},{"id":"114011","num":5}],[{"id":"2","num":8000},{"id":"110211","num":3},{"id":"114011","num":10}],[{"id":"2","num":16000},{"id":"110212","num":3},{"id":"114012","num":6}],[{"id":"2","num":40000},{"id":"110212","num":6},{"id":"114012","num":9}],[{"id":"2","num":80000},{"id":"110213","num":4},{"id":"114013","num":5}],[{"id"